description:
&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent opportunity to work within the Research &amp; Development administrative team, based at the Royal Sussex County Hospital in Brighton. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking to recruit a full-time receptionist, based in the Clinical Research Facility. The Clinical Research Facility is a state of the art, patient-centred research environment that offers bespoke facilities for clinical researchers. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This particular appointment is required to provide the reception &amp; administrative support that ensures the smooth-running of unit. The post holder will provide a friendly, professional and efficient reception service to patients &amp; visitors attending the unit, for a variety of clinical specialties as well as assisting with clerical duties associated with patients attending the department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameCarla ChambersJob titleResearch Administration &amp; Data Team LeadEmail addresscarla.chambers@nhs.netTelephone number01273 696955 ext 3522&lt;/p&gt;
